Watchlist

Where to Watch

In this ingenious thriller infused with a wickedly dark sense of humor, the lives of several seemingly unrelated people intersect one night in a sleepy small town because of a car accident. The great ensemble cast includes Oscar-winner Hilary Swank, Henry Thomas, Barbara Hershey, Clark Gregg, Shawn Hatosy, Colin Hanks, Ben Foster and Patrick Swayze. Greg Marcks directed and wrote the screenplay.
